{"about_the_game":"<strong>Bricks of Camels</strong> brings creative minds together in a competitive arena where you control animal characters to build structures using brick-like pieces. Whether you\u2019re a camel, a donkey, or a GOAT, each animal has its unique style and personality, making your building experience as delightful as it is challenging!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHOOSE YOUR CHARACTER</h2>Pick from a variety of animal characters and let your creativity run wild.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/choosechar_gif.gif?t=1726952430\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">RACE AGAINST TIME</h2>At the start of each game, a common word is given, and you have only 5 minutes to build your best interpretation.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/raceagainst_gif.gif?t=1726952430\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VOTE</h2>Once time\u2019s up, players vote on each other\u2019s creations to determine the winner.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/new_voting_gif.gif?t=1726952430\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WIN AND CONQUER</h2>The player with the most votes wins the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176940/extras/win_gif.gif?t=1726952430\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Place Bricks: 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3176940/523f0e2882d30d5cc415d3ef6e1068f2617d9eff.jpg"},{"name":" Place Bricks: 10","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3176940/d9ae71e972cf6279872a27b5808ee77e79bff5ec.jpg"},{"name":"Place Bricks: 100","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3176940/f28df8d252fa99bf96fdd0f506ce28ffdb4c6d85.jpg"},{"name":"Place Bricks: 1000","path":"https://cdn.akamai.st